  ('Chicken Licken', 'Fast Food Chain', '1 000+ employees', 'Johannesburg (HQ) · Nationwide', 'Chicken Licken is one of South Africa''s most beloved home-grown fast food chains, famous for Soul Fire chicken and iconic advertising. With 280+ restaurants, it''s a distinctly South African brand that resonates deeply with local culture. Founded in 1981, Chicken Licken remains proudly independent.', 'chickenlicken.co.za', 'https://logo.clearbit.com/chickenlicken.co.za', true),
