  ('Panarottis Pizza Pasta', 'Casual Dining Chain', '201–500 employees', 'Cape Town (HQ) · Nationwide', 'Panarottis is a South African casual dining brand known for its all-you-can-eat salad bar, deep-dish and thin-crust pizzas, and pasta. Part of the Spur Corporation group, Panarottis operates 80+ restaurants, primarily in shopping malls, and targets family diners seeking Italian-inspired comfort food.', 'panarottis.co.za', 'https://logo.clearbit.com/panarottis.co.za', true),
